### GET all books
GET https://my-flask-json-api.onrender.com/books
Accept: application/json

###

### POST a new book
POST https://my-flask-json-api.onrender.com/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Learn Flask",
  "author": "Alice",
  "price": 299.99,
  "in_stock": true
}

###

### PUT update book at index 0
PUT https://my-flask-json-api.onrender.com/books/0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Master Flask",
  "author": "Bob",
  "price": 349.99,
  "in_stock": false
}

###

### DELETE book at index 0
DELETE https://my-flask-json-api.onrender.com/books/0
Accept: application/json
